SecondPassHandler

SecondPassHandler(java.lang.Object verb, java.lang.Object handler, java.lang.Object width, java.lang.Object height, java.lang.Object inst, java.lang.Object oFile, java.lang.Object percentile, java.lang.Object range, java.lang.Object pageSize, java.lang.Object gridMarks, java.lang.Object boost)
Calculate and draw the memory reference map
Parameters:
verb - verbose output
handler - contains basic information about lackeyml file
width - width of graph in pixels
height - height of graph in pixels
inst - plot instructions
oFile - path to output file
percentile - percentile to begin plot with
range - range of percentiles to plot
pageSize - page size to use
gridMarks - grid lines to draw
boost - margin size in pixels
